videos.description: The Shockers had four different players score on their 10-0 run to tie the game against Tulsa 30-30.
videos.headline: Wichita State goes on 10-0 run

videos.description: Landry Shamet gets open and drills a 3-pointer with a defender in his face for the and-1.
videos.headline: Shockers' Shamet gets a 4-point play

videos.description: Tulsa's Sterling Taplin had a chance to tie the game after purposefully missing a free throw but failed to convert the 3-point attempt.
videos.headline: Crazy sequence ends in Tulsa loss
